                                tr
                                    td For Jesus sake
                                    td: input(type="text" class="c-input js-escribir" )
                    .col.xs12.md6
                        h6 Shared possession is indicated by a single apostrophe.
                        ul.lh25
                            li #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Robert Smith and Rebecca Green’s drama play. (They coauthored the play)
                            li #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Sara and Nick’s house. (They share the house)

                        h6 Individual possession is indicated by apostrophes for each possessor.
                        ul.lh25
                            li #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Colombia’s and Chile’s domestic policies are diverging.
                            li #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Camila’s and Adriana’s houses were designed by the same person.

